titles.title: A resolution recognizing Kikkoman Foods, Inc., for its 50 years of operations in the United States.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on the Judiciary.

bill.summary:
9/20/2007--Introduced.
Commends Kikkoman Foods, Inc., on its 50 years of marketing and operations in the United States. Recognizes its contributions to U.S. cultural and economic vitality.
